***  Single NMOS and PMOS Transistor BSIM3 (Id-Vgs, Vbs) (Id-Vds, Vgs) (Id-Vgs, T)  ***

M1 2 1 3 4 n1 W=1u L=0.35u Pd=1.5u Ps=1.5u ad=1.5p as=1.5p
vgsn 1 0 3.5
vdsn 2 0 0.1
vssn 3 0 0
vbsn 4 0 0

M2 22 11 33 44 p1 W=2.5u L=0.35u Pd=3u Ps=3u ad=2.5p as=2.5p
vgsp 11 0 -3.5
vdsp 22 0 -0.1
vssp 33 0 0
vbsp 44 0 0

